What is Class:
  Class is simply a file that contains a lot of things methods is one of them.
  Each method contains code to do something.When we want our pc to dat task,we create
   the object of class ,and  we call that method.
Method:
   method is a block of code that performs a specific task or action.
   It's a reusable piece of code that can be called from other parts
   of a program. Methods are used to organize code into logical
   units, improve code readability, and facilitate code reuse.
